<p>You can <a href="https://protesilaos.com/hsw/">read the book online</a> or visit its
<a href="https://protesilaos.com/hsw/print/">print-optimised page</a> to get a physical copy.</p>

<p>Maybe you will enjoy reading it as much as I did writing it. Feel
free to <a href="https://protesilaos.com/contact/">contact me</a> if you have any comments or found
something that does not seem right.</p>